invariants:
 - IIPS: the floating confetti should be decorative, above the profile image in the card, using the existing asset.
 - The asset is /assets/img/Confetti.png (exists in public/assets/img/).
 - Position it as floating above the profile pic (inside the relative profile container or with correct absolute to appear above it).
 - Keep the animation .hadacard-confetti-anim if present.
 - No other changes to the card or other states.
